metadata.name: Hellbangers #002
metadata.description: Hellbangers #002 is part of the Hellbangers series, a collection of 111 1/1 NFT by award-winning artist Pep Bonet. Celebrating music, passion, freedom and togetherness, Hellbangers explores the metal scene in Botswana.
